由于手头上做一些情感分析相关的研究，最近在研究您的代码，目前存在两个问题，向您请教，如下：
1. 我输入"我爱南方航空" 分词分成 "南方" 和 "航空",这类问题怎么优化；
2. 输出情感值的时候使用的是bayes输出概率，核心代码如下
def classify(self, x):
        print str(x).decode("unicode-escape")
        tmp = {}
        for k in self.d:
            print self.d
            tmp[k] = log(self.d[k].getsum()) - log(self.total)
            for word in x:
                tmp[k] += log(self.d[k].freq(word))
        ret, prob = 0, 0
        for k in self.d:
            now = 0
            try:
                for otherk in self.d:
                    now += exp(tmp[otherk]-tmp[k])
                now = 1/now
            except OverflowError:
                now = 0
            if now > prob:
                ret, prob = k, now
        return (ret, prob)
我看了下，输入的是分词后的结果，那么bayes是怎么样将文本直接输出概率呢，代码有点没看懂，谢谢！

In _send_upstream() [base.py](https://github.com/dpkp/kafka-python/blob/master/kafka/producer/base.py#L135) (master branch), 

        # Send collected requests upstream
        for topic_partition, msg in msgset.items():
            messages = create_message_set(msg, codec, key, codec_compresslevel)

Note that the **key** parameter passed to create_message_set() is used in the above [**while** loop](https://github.com/dpkp/kafka-python/blob/master/kafka/producer/base.py#L119)

        while count > 0 and timeout >= 0:
            try:
                topic_partition, msg, key = queue.get(timeout=timeout)
            except Empty:
                break

Does it make sense?

